{"tid":1432033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警察記招 令廢老師奶相信外國勢力輸入高科技鐳射槍 亂港","createTime":"2019-08-08T06:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T11:44:10.000Z","uid":294333,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"02cfea86e2a6f22149d8dcb5694373b416c84f75","tid":1432033,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:35:53.000Z","msg":"今日搭巴士，飲咗陣茶， 聽到廢老師奶睇微信朋友圈，班後生暴徒鐳射槍高殺傷力武器射傷警察，又縱火殺警署，肯定有外國勢力洗腦亂港。<br />\n<br />\n有廢老和應：中排$1200，前線$3000，被差人拉有$5000，日日搞事塞馬路好搵過返暑假工。<br />\n唔上進買唔到樓嘅廢青淨係識搞亂香港， 星期一塞車呀，搞唔到我出嚟搭車飲茶。 如果我仲後生，燒9佢老味冚家剷！<br />\n<br />\n另外師奶搭嘴：你班夠後生玩咩，人哋拎住美國佬枝鐳射槍射死你，哈哈哈！"},{"pid":"e0cf12d950ec5aa9b5a3c583a12ccf4a1551ffd4","tid":1432033,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:36:16.000Z","msg":"廢老係咁嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c283662c174699843b71bfa480cc4c0d3d031c9","tid":1432033,"uid":124048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824735ac83580b7050478eb7a81015a2afbea66c","tid":1432033,"uid":201374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:37:45.000Z","msg":"哩啲廢老一日唔食幾粒催淚彈，一日唔俾黑警扑穿頭，一日都唔係醒<br />\n放棄啦"},{"pid":"ce75dcd8168c0d37e6a2db4859c2f910aa8fc104","tid":1432033,"uid":196861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:38:09.000Z","msg":"唔洗理喲唔用腦嘅人啦<br />\n你點解釋佢都唔會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac8860043237115c645cd8fe033ba49d4af3de5","tid":1432033,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"人形豬有得食訓屙就得啦"},{"pid":"2514f14d8c002d8e1bfdafccca8542d051e908bf","tid":1432033,"uid":263583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:56:05.000Z","msg":"重點係你有樓未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909f446c97630